snippet: Wall Street closed mixed, staying close to multiyear highs for stock indexes. While some analysts continue to see an upward bias, recent daily moves have been small.
abstract: Stock market lacks direction as slump in McDonald's stock helps pull Dow Jones industrial average below 14,000.
lead_paragraph: Wall Street closed mixed, staying close to multiyear highs for stock indexes. While some analysts continue to see an upward bias, recent daily moves have been small.

headline.main: Decline in McDonald’s Sends Dow Lower; S.&P. and Nasdaq Rise
headline.print_headline: Decline in McDonald’s Sends Dow Lower; S.&P. and Nasdaq Rise
